--- In nbwrpg@y..., "CYBERWOLF4" <cyberwolf4@p...> wrote:
> Dogged looked at the bums chest, he'd thrown his hardest punch and barely
> left a scratch that was already beginning to repair itself. He sensed a
> shadow hovering over him. "Oh SH..." his thoughts were cut off by a fist
> slamming down on his head forcing him to the ground. (This might be moding
> but I think you'll like it.) The bums fist continued downward striking the
> ground, Dogged still between the fist and the pavement. When the fist raised
> Doggeds crushed body lay with only it's feet fully intact and hanging out of
> the hole. Sparks flashed from the rest of it as all motor functions ceased.
